    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>見たか！
これが『なりきり士』の力だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>See that!? That's the power
of a Roleplayer!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私が息絶えたとしても
我が一族は、あなたたちへの
追撃の手を緩めません！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even if you managed to sentence me to
death, my subordinates would chase you
down to the very edges of hell.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>プルートにそう伝えなさい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Make Pluto aware of that!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぐっ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279268</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ……追わなくてもいいの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Umm... Shouldn't we
chase after him?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>構いません。
私たちの今の目的は
彼を倒すことではないのですから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Worry not. Right now, our objective
is not to defeat that enemy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279492</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Suzu&gt;ちゃん、
かっこおもしろいよ！
さすが時空戦士だな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Suzu&gt; you're so rad! No wonder you're
one of the Heroes of Time!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279560</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クゥールール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuruu!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>かっこ……
何ですか、それ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Rad...? What is the
meaning of that word?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>かっこいいってこと、
だよね？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Rad as in radical, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>堂々としてて、
凛としてて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Because you're so calculating with
your actions, and you're so elegant
with your words...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279936</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしが侮られるというのは
一族が侮られるということ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Taking me lightly is taking lightly
the responsibility of my people.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279936</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それは、一族全体の士気にも
関わってきます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My actions affect the morale of
the entirety of the ninja clan.
I must uphold that responsibility.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280036</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すごいな。オレらなんて
自分のことで精一杯なのに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's awesome, you know?
That just makes me wanna
try harder. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280684</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうしたんですか、
&lt;Rody&gt;さん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you doing, Miss &lt;Rody&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　あ、ううん、
なんでもないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah, oh, this? It's nothing!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280868</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……それ、
誰かからのプレゼント、
ですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That ring... That's a gift
from someone, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まぁね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sorta, I guess...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281268</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さ、行こう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, let's move.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_200_010_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの指輪……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That ring...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
